  "title": "🎉 Fun Sales & Marketing Crew – Join the Hype Team! ⚡",
  "description": "<p>Are you energetic, talkative, and love being around people? If you enjoy fast-paced environments, hyping up products, and closing sales — this is YOUR opportunity! 🤩</p><p>Join our <strong>Fun Sales & Marketing Crew</strong> and be part of exciting roadshows, and promotional campaigns across Singapore! </p><p>⭐ What You’ll Do</p><ul><li>Engage customers with confidence, positivity & product knowledge</li><li>Promote brands through interactive pitch & product storytelling</li><li>Help drive sales </li><li>Build real connections and deliver memorable customer experiences</li><li>Work closely with a supportive crew + team leaders 🎯</li></ul><h3>💼 What You’ll Gain</h3><ul><li><strong>Weekly Pay</strong> 💵 + Bonuses & Incentives</li><li>Hands-on Marketing & Sales experience</li><li>Communication, negotiation & teamwork superpowers</li><li>A fun work culture filled with laughter & growth 🚀</li><li>Flexible schedules — weekdays & weekends available</li></ul><h3>💡 Who We’re Looking For</h3><ul><li>Outgoing, energetic & loves talking to people</li><li>Team player with a positive, can-do attitude</li><li>Adaptable in a fast-paced environment</li><li>No experience? No problem — training provided! 🔥</li></ul><p>🎯 <strong>If you’re a people-person with big energy and sales ambition… WE WANT YOU!</strong><br />Apply now & let’s make every event UNFORGETTABLE together ✨💃🛍️</p>",
